{"tid":197765,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"雷神3 預告日點擊達1.36億，打破迪士尼記錄","createTime":"2017-04-12T05:49:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T14:43:05.000Z","uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a07ddcc03353abd9d41ee29aeaf10b70be1834de","tid":197765,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T05:49:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://screenrant1.imgix.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Thor-Ragnarok-Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscreenrant1.imgix.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2FThor-Ragnarok-Poster.jpg&h=c3d1c3d2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n<br />\r\n根據《hollywoodreporter》報導，迪士尼發行的Marvel英雄電影《雷神3：諸神黃昏》前導預告片，其發布24小時內的播放量達1.36億，打破此前迪士尼系列電影的紀錄，《美女與野獸》預告片的1.276億。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n據悉，之前迪士尼的紀錄由《星球大戰7》的1.12億保持，Marvel電影則為之前《美國隊長3：內戰》的9400萬。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n本次《雷神3》的播放量則一舉成為迪士尼所有類型電影預告片播放量第一，當然包括全球超級英雄第一，DC英雄電影預告片播放量均未上億。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n縱觀所有廠商全類型電影播放量，其中第一保持者為3月29日發布的2017新版《靈異魔咒》預告片，其24小時內播放量達1.97億，然後為《狂野時速8》預告片的1.39億，毫無意外的話，《雷神3》憑藉1.36億應該為第三。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n另外，《雷神3》預告片反應如此勁爆，除了雷神之鎚被粉碎，雷神大戰變形俠醫外，預告片的背景音樂更成為大大重點，正是英國搖滾鼻祖樂隊Led Zeppelin(齊柏林飛船)的經典代表作Immigrant Song。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n傳聞《雷神3》這支預告片成本為500萬美金，其中編輯製作費用10萬美金，最貴部分則為Immigrant Song的版權費，竟高達490萬美金，不清楚是否正片採用這個音樂，Marvel非常會選歌，因為Immigrant Song正是描述北歐神話的歌。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/thor-ragnarok-trailer-is-marvel-disneys-watched-ever-24-hours-992978\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Fheat-vision%2Fthor-ragnarok-trailer-is-marvel-disneys-watched-ever-24-hours-992978&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppehxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=4c91f9e2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/thor-ragnarok-trailer-is-marvel-disneys-watched-ever-24-hours-992978</a> <br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=_qrhyaasBXo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_qrhyaasBXo&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppehxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=faecaa44\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=_qrhyaasBXo</a>"},{"pid":"eef8bf5f0e15da956f117c9d566a9ab8f4c6fa9f","tid":197765,"uid":55657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T05:51:23.000Z","msg":"個字體同銀河守護隊好似一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f57650f1c22a95f19997f8dc772b306e5ca6183","tid":197765,"uid":61279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T05:54:18.000Z","msg":"首歌既版權竟然要咁貴，估唔到 wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce3b2675a8dcbb9f237073d43860f0f587090199","tid":197765,"uid":33734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T06:02:45.000Z","msg":"整個預告都要500萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a8dfded96e3d1b808e64f8dd330f3bce4ba33dd","tid":197765,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T06:08:04.000Z","msg":"貴過一套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75672e60ae786373e1066a43fd0ca7ce86b19ebb","tid":197765,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T06:12:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首歌既版權竟然要咁貴，估唔到 wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n投資正確"},{"pid":"e363443d07eb050eb06580396d0412debbef57c3","tid":197765,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T06:17:03.000Z","msg":"咁搞法會唔會票房高過英雄內戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0e2126478de5388e276f348868f103f88f06a1a","tid":197765,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T06:19:51.000Z","msg":"我地識架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfacbb592b1ebd2f052e36a7bb4fc294ebec5bd9","tid":197765,"uid":52881,"like":0,"